      "writtenOn": "2020-03-04T21:52:13Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "You\u0027re right. I only plan to make a POST request to /json/triage (see followup CL: https://skia-review.googlesource.com/c/buildbot/+/269538), which isn\u0027t idempotent as it will insert a new triage log entry every time.\n\nUnless you can think of a good reason to keep this, I\u0027ll abandon the postWithRetries code and call the RPC with one single try.\n\nPlease let me know your thoughts.",
      "parentUuid": "7b2fa6c3_de8b6c50",
      "revId": "d69c610fabc1e07b38942fa10aee83e364e56d27",
